# Cached station extract + intermediates — regenerable from data/raw via `make prepare`.
# (Raw .csv.gz in data/raw/ ARE kept; they are the compressed source of truth.)
data/processed/

# Generated analysis outputs — rebuilt by `make all`
# (kept out of version control; the report is the shareable artifact you copy out)
outputs/figures/
outputs/annual_temperatures.csv
# Note: outputs/temperature_report.html is the deliverable — commit it if you
#       want the rendered report tracked; otherwise it stays ignored below.
outputs/temperature_report.html

# R session cruft
.Rhistory
.RData
.Rproj.user/
*.Rproj

# macOS
.DS_Store
